an integrate a skybox into RC by merging the sky integral into the highest =
angular resolution cascade (because skyboxes have little to no linear resol=
ution being extremely far from the =E2=80=9Csun=E2=80=9D). This does not af=
fect occlusion either so it really does act like an actual skybox! We=E2=80=
